The useEffect hook is missing `isGridInEditMode` in its dependency array. This could lead to stale closure issues.

```typescript
useEffect(() => {
  // existing code
}, [isGridInEditMode, otherDeps]);
```

Consider adding a dependency array to this useEffect hook to avoid running on every render:

```typescript
useEffect(() => {
  if (gridApi) {
    gridApi.refreshCells();
  }
}, [gridApi]);
```

The `pipelinesTableLayout` constant appears to be identical to `modernTableLayout`. Consider consolidating:

```typescript
// Remove pipelinesTableLayout and use modernTableLayout instead
export const tableLayouts = {
  modern: modernTableLayout,
  pipelines: modernTableLayout, // alias for backwards compatibility
};
```

